Package: SCneighbours
Type: Package
Title: Single-Cell Neighbourhood Exploration Tool
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("First", "Last", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for visualizing and quantifying cell neighbourhoods in
    single-cell RNA sequencing data. Provides functions to visualize cell
    neighbourhoods as dots or density contours on dimensionality reduction
    maps, quantify neighbourhood distributions by variance in coordinates,
    and explore neighbourhoods across various dimensionality reductions.
